ment-with-china-over-fishermens-deaths-2024-07-30/</link><description>经过几个月的谈判，台湾与中国周二就两名中国渔民在海事事件中丧生一事达成协议，此举可能会缓和敏感的台湾海峡的紧张局势。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 05:51:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-says-reaches-agreement-with-china-over-fishermens-deaths-2024-07-30/</guid></item><item><title>贸易部长称印度不会重新考虑允许中国投资的问题</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/india-not-rethinking-issue-allowing-chinese-investment-trade-minister-says-2024-07-30/</link><description>印度贸易部长皮尤什·戈亚尔周二表示，印度不会重新考虑允许中国投资的问题。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 05:28:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/india/india-not-rethinking-issue-allowing-chinese-investment-trade-minister-says-2024-07-30/</guid></item><item><title>意大利总理梅洛尼：中国对俄罗斯战争努力的支持是“巨大摩擦”的根源</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/italys-meloni-chinas-support-russian-war-effort-source-great-friction-2024-07-30/</link><description>意大利总理乔治亚·梅洛尼周二在对中国进行正式访问时表示，中国对俄罗斯对乌克兰战争的经济支持是“巨大摩擦”的根源。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 05:12:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/italys-meloni-chinas-support-russian-war-effort-source-great-friction-2024-07-30/</guid></item><item><title>副总理：中国的“新生产力”需要政府和市场的共同努力</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-new-productive-forces-need-government-market-efforts-vice-premier-2024-07-30/</link><description>官方媒体周二称，中国副总理何立峰强调，需要一个协调良好的政府和有效的市场来发展国家的“新生产力”。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 03:28:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-new-productive-forces-need-government-market-efforts-vice-premier-2024-07-30/</guid></item><item><title>台风余波带来降雨和洪水，中国四人死亡</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/four-killed-rains-floods-remnants-weakened-gaemi-lash-south-china-2024-07-30/</link><description>官方媒体周二称，中国南部省份湖南省因台风“盖米”残余降雨量创纪录，暴雨和洪水造成四人死亡，数千人被迫撤离家园。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 03:07:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/four-killed-rains-floods-remnants-weakened-gaemi-lash-south-china-2024-07-30/</guid></item><item><title>马科斯表示，美国与菲律宾的接触有助于对中国做出“敏捷”反应</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/us-philippines-engagements-help-with-agile-responses-china-says-marcos-2024-07-30/</link><description>菲律宾总统小费迪南德·马科斯周二告诉美国内阁秘书安东尼·布林肯和劳埃德·奥斯汀，马尼拉和华盛顿之间需要定期接触，以确保“灵活”应对菲律宾与中国的海上紧张局势。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 02:19:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/us-philippines-engagements-help-with-agile-responses-china-says-marcos-2024-07-30/</guid></item><item><title>油价因中国需求担忧而下滑，中东担忧消退</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/oil-prices-slip-china-demand-concerns-waning-middle-east-worries-2024-07-30/</link><description>由于对全球最大原油进口国中国需求的担忧，油价周二下跌，延续了前一交易日的跌幅，而市场则摆脱了中东冲突升级的风险。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 01:04:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/oil-prices-slip-china-demand-concerns-waning-middle-east-worries-2024-07-30/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：美联储、日本央行面前的等待游戏</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-07-29/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 21:48:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-07-29/</guid></item><item><title>体操-日本队在激动人心的决赛中击败中国队夺得男子团体金牌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/gymnastics-japan-win-mens-team-gold-2024-07-29/</link><description>桥本大树周一在巴黎奥运会体操男子团体决赛中战胜了中国队，从鞍马上摔倒，最终夺得金牌，他将心痛变成了难以想象的喜悦。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 18:14:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/gymnastics-japan-win-mens-team-gold-2024-07-29/</guid></item><item><title>情报官员称，外国势力将寻求影响重塑的美国总统竞选</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/foreign-influence-actors-adapt-us-presidential-race-changes-says-intelligence-2024-07-29/</link><description>一名美国情报官员周一表示，针对 11 月大选进行影响力行动的美国敌人预计将适应总统竞选的发展，这显然是指乔·拜登放弃连任竞选。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 17:22:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/foreign-influence-actors-adapt-us-presidential-race-changes-says-intelligence-2024-07-29/</guid></item><item><title>独家：SpaceX 正在洽谈在澳大利亚海岸着陆并回收星舰火箭</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/space/spacex-talks-land-recover-starship-rocket-off-australias-coast-2024-07-29/</link><description>据三位知情人士透露，SpaceX 正在与美国和澳大利亚官员进行谈判，以在澳大利亚海岸着陆并回收其一艘 Starship 火箭，这可能是埃隆·马斯克 (Elon Musk) 的公司在该地区扩大业务的第一步，因为两国加强了安全关系。与计划。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 17:05:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/space/spacex-talks-land-recover-starship-rocket-off-australias-coast-2024-07-29/</guid></item><item><title>中国间谍还是反革命？外国特工审判在布鲁克林开始</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/legal/trial-begins-us-citizen-accused-acting-chinese-agent-2024-07-29/</link><description>美国检方指控一名中国学者在周一对这位 76 岁的外国特工指控的审判开始时向北京出卖了美国的异见人士，而辩护律师则表示，他们的当事人正试图为共产主义中国带来民主。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 16:44:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/legal/trial-begins-us-citizen-accused-acting-chinese-agent-2024-07-29/</guid></item></channel></rss>